= Ri18n Changelog

== Version 0.0.3

* Wrote USAGE documentation
* A bit of code cleanup and refactoring
* Not-gem packages use setup.rb for installation 
* write gettext compatible PO headers; 
  You can now use POedit (or other translation tools) to work on PO files. 
* add Rake::GettextTask for defining a gettext task in a more standard way

== Version 0.0.2

* first charset conversion support (with iconv)
* read/parse/save/write of PO headers
* keep comments in PO files intact when updating
* Support single quotes in translation strings

== Version 0.0.1

* Initial release

